## Migrations

```php
class m210101_000000_create_user extends Migration
{
    public function up()
    {
        $this->createTable('{{%user}}', [
            'id' => $this->primaryKey(),
            'username' => $this->string(255)->notNull()->unique(),
            'created_at' => $this->integer()->notNull(),
        ]);
    }

    public function down()
    {
        $this->dropTable('{{%user}}');
    }
}
```

